<h4><strong>Absence Management</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>Immediate Slack integration &#x2013; if you use Slack as a collaboration tool, you can plug in flair for seamless attendance management and approvals.</li>
<li>Manage overtime and vacation requests and check on the status of jobs to understand how your employees like to work.</li>
<li>Filter absences based on multiple locations, teams, absence types, and time frames.</li>
<li>Integrate your absences calendar with Google Calendar, Microsoft Outlook, and iCal.</li>
</ul>
<h4><strong>Time Tracking &amp; Shift Planner</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>Tracking flexible work hours just got easier: Managers can assign flexible hours, and employees can log their time at work using the<a href="https://flair.hr/en/time-tracking" rel="noopener"> Time Tracking</a> tool.</li>
<li>Empower shift workers to choose hours that suit them with the Open Shifts feature. Leave notes on shifts for smooth asynchronous communication.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><img src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/JQ7ESPStGZr1NHGG9dlfDiJ1k3mVWZoF5yANSOgCJxwIltTH6WzfUogHtDIdPYrEWD3FSAKM8YPKNRiA8OPuZ1VY5hrjlbThmbJV-gajBqL6x5MZaipCSgWWCuPHw9FGasT5rDabKdT6U0-fMaqqUw" alt></strong></p>
